挑选”过的画面（如下图），开始讲述“疫情下中国的严格管制对个人的影响”了…"},"attached_info":"Cj8IjpH096GV8oAREAMaCDY1MzcwMTA4IM71/IUGMBI4iQRABHIJNDYzOTA3OTA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"508 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3c07121b37343464d757a1f04aac01f9_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1623204780.5027587","card_id":"Q_447920355","target":{"id":447920355,"title":"买房时要避开哪些楼层？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/447920355","type":"question","created":1615022020,"answer_count":301,"follower_count":5133,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[525,3254,3865,114392],"comment_count":20,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IjpH096GV8oAREAMaCDYxODE2NDg1IMSPjYIGMBQ4jShABXIJNDQ3OTIwMzU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"466 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-43f4b6542e600e32689712c582dc66dc_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1623204780.5033164","card_id":"Q_463156456","target":{"id":463156456,"title":"「睾丸是和大脑最像的人体器官」这一结论有什么实际意义么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/463156456","type":"question","created":1622806464,"answer_count":605,"follower_count":2555,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2232,8437,19730,23174,105575],"comment_count":75,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，一研究对比了 33 种人体组织中的蛋白，覆盖心脏、肠道、子宫颈、卵巢和胎盘，发现睾丸和大脑中相同的蛋白达到了 13,442 种。「与其他身体组织相比，大脑和睾丸中共同的蛋白质数量最多」，葡萄牙阿威罗大学（University of Aveiro）的生物医学科学家 Bárbara Matos 团队在这篇论文中写道。相关论文 2021 年 6 月 2 日在英国皇家学会Open Biology期刊发表。睾丸是与大脑最相似的人体器官，它们共享10000多种蛋白质"},"attached_info":"Cj8IjpH096GV8oAREAMaCDY1MjAzMzE0IMCf6IUGMEs4+xNABnIJNDYzMTU2NDU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","det